{"tid":2162064,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉股價新高 Elon Musk成為全球第4大富豪","createTime":"2020-08-18T02:26:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T06:31:18.000Z","uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1b65704dd46650af8d79263a23e50d85462d8188","tid":2162064,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:26:30.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕特斯拉股價週一（17日）再飆新高，收漲11.2%、每股漲破1800美元，帶動執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）身價大增78億美元，成為全球第4大億萬富翁。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，馬斯克目前身價已超越法國奢侈品大亨阿諾特（Bernard Arnault），以150億美元的差距緊追全球第3大富豪祖克柏（Mark Zuckerberg）。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n據報導，馬斯克今年財富增加572億美元，為彭博億萬富翁指數中增幅第2大，僅次於亞馬遜執行長貝佐斯（Jeff Bezos）的730億美元增幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3263412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3263412&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=2b3c3265\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3263412&h=6b29fed3\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3263412</a>"},{"pid":"a8a6743ee423658e86c51bceaecbd02bd2d497d6","tid":2162064,"uid":75432,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"今晚就追到第三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"564f13208caeb2f3143c3e25875043b0d9579166","tid":2162064,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8a6743ee423658e86c51bceaecbd02bd2d497d6","tid":2162064,"uid":75432,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"今晚就追到第三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T02:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=